{"tid":1927930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知點先贏到","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:55:47.000Z","uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c45726f2f766dd89c0ceab709977cef07accba5","tid":1927930,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"很多人問我，連登那麼多膠po廢文， 令到熱門很多不是抗爭相關的po， 運動是不是要輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是小編找到了連登這個很多人都不知道的隱藏設定， 一分鐘內就能令你不再看到膠po廢文，令運動重上正軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先按設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPG0aFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPG0aFX.jpg&h=3199bed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後找自選台設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydmLmNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydmLmNW.jpg&h=d8c80351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再揀選你心儀的台， 譬如小編揀的就是時事台和政事台， 選擇完按右上角的✔儲存設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WdTxMff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdTxMff.jpg&h=f0176a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再返回設定按預設討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3zH8tQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3zH8tQ.jpg&h=757c5578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選擇你剛才設定的自選台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55HOjAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55HOjAV.png&h=f2ba9db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後重啟連登應用程式，嘩！膠po廢文都不見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PdhXn6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PdhXn6.png&h=98aad639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成這個設定後每次你進入連登都不會再見到膠po廢文， 讓你全心全力投入革命和抗爭<br />\n<br />\n小編今天的介紹就到此為止<br />\n認同請正評及分享<br />\n好人一生平安🙏<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"780f10e676ef8cc345902bd383cb220286e61963","tid":1927930,"uid":224196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"之後班mon po狗就會係政治台同時事台係咁開淫post"}]}